description:

Each card is packed with a white envelope in a bio-degradeable cornstarch bag. 

The selection of six is taken from the most popular images in the print range, and may vary from the designs shown.

Or choose your own selection from the prints available, and send a separate email or list them in the PayPal comments box when you pay.
